at.tugraz.kmi.medokyservice.fca.lib.colibri.lib

Class Edge

  • java.lang.Object
    • at.tugraz.kmi.medokyservice.fca.lib.colibri.lib.Edge

  • public class Edge
extends java.lang.Object
    Representation of a pair of concepts that are neighbors of each other in a concept lattice. By definition a concept u is the upper neighbor of a concept l in a concept lattice, iff the object set of l is a strict subset of the object set of u and there exists no other concept c in the lattice such that the object set of l is a strict subset of the object set of c and the object set of c is a strict subset of the object set of u.
    Version:
    1.0
    Author:
    Daniel N. Goetzmann
